### Variables
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7001
@apiVersion = 1

### Get All Plants
GET {{baseUrl}}/v{{apiVersion}}/Plants
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Plant By Id
@plantId = 1f4820b1-21a6-4fe4-8dad-b886fab90f8b
GET {{baseUrl}}/v{{apiVersion}}/Plants/{{plantId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Create Plant
PUT {{baseUrl}}/v{{apiVersion}}/Plants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "commonName": "Fiddle Leaf Fig",
  "scientificName": "Ficus carica",
  "duration": "Perennial",
  "age": 1,
  "url": "https://plants.usda.gov/plant-profile/FICA"
}

###

### Update Plant By Id
@updatePlantId = 1f4820b1-21a6-4fe4-8dad-b886fab90f8b
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/v{{apiVersion}}/Plants/{{updatePlantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "duration": "Annual",
  "age": 3,
}

###

### Delete Plant By Id
@deletePlantId = 1f4820b1-21a6-4fe4-8dad-b886fab90f8b
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/v{{apiVersion}}/Plants/{{deletePlantId}}

